    <item>
      <title>墨西哥称美国推迟征收关税后谷物价格出现逆转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/grains-jump-in-reversal-after-mexico-says-us-tariffs-delayed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆表示美国对拉丁美洲国家产品征收关税将推迟一个月，随后玉米和小麦期货走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/grains-jump-in-reversal-after-mexico-says-us-tariffs-delayed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:48:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥向投资者保证其经济能够承受关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-finance-chief-tells-investors-it-can-withstand-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥财政部长表示，墨西哥已采取措施保护其经济免受美国关税冲击，并且各部门正在共同努力，以防货币市场的流动性受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-finance-chief-tells-investors-it-can-withstand-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:01:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安大略省取消 Starlink 协议，禁止美国公司签订政府合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ontario-cancels-starlink-contract-won-t-do-deals-with-us-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安大略省省长表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普发布行政命令，对从加拿大进口的商品征收关税，安大略省政府将终止与埃隆·马斯克控制的卫星公司 Starlink 的合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ontario-cancels-starlink-contract-won-t-do-deals-with-us-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 13:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚勇敢面对市场动荡，通过出售外汇债券填补缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/romania-starts-fx-debt-sales-to-plug-deficit-amid-global-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚今年首次进入国际资本市场，在国内政局和全球投资者情绪动荡之际筹集新债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/romania-starts-fx-debt-sales-to-plug-deficit-amid-global-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 11:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国暂缓特朗普关税威胁，英镑上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/pound-gets-boost-on-uk-s-reprieve-from-trump-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的贸易关税，全球金融市场紧张情绪不断升温，英镑因此意外成为避风港。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/pound-gets-boost-on-uk-s-reprieve-from-trump-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 11:16:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥比索引领新兴市场外汇反弹，因 Sheinbaum 称关税推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆与唐纳德·特朗普通话后表示，美国对墨西哥征收关税将推迟一个月，随后墨西哥比索领涨新兴市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场显示担忧关税将引发通胀和经济增长冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国债券市场向总统唐纳德·特朗普发出警告，称他对主要贸易伙伴加征关税的举措可能会加剧通胀并减缓美国经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥关税推迟一个月，欧洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希恩鲍姆与唐纳德·特朗普通话后表示，美国将推迟一个月实施对华关税，欧洲股市随后缩减了早前的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:53:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美墨关税希望升温，股市脱离低点：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普确认，他与墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆就立即暂停征收关税一个月一事达成一致，墨西哥比索抹去了损失，股市从盘中低点回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
